To plot indicator values, in the OnData event handler, call the Plot method.

private Maximum _max;

// In Initialize()
var symbol = AddEquity("SPY").Symbol;
_max = MAX(symbol, period);

// In OnData()
if (_max.IsReady)
{
    Plot("My Indicators", "maximum", _max.Current.Value);
}
